data.description: Don't miss out on this stunning mid-century ranch-style classic boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Situated on a spacious corner lot in the Wareingwood area of Dalraida, this home offers ample shade from mature trees, keeping it cool during the warm Alabama Summers. The main bedroom includes its own bath, complemented by a full hallway bath. Roof (2020), HVAC system (2020), New Water Heater (2023) and stainless steel kitchen appliances. The kitchen features a breakfast bar and separate breakfast nook, while the dining room provides ample space for family gatherings. The flexible front living room can serve various purposes, while the den/family room at the back of the house offers a cozy fireplace and a view of the beautiful backyard. Outside, enjoy the wooden deck and new gas grill for family gatherings, along with a wired detached storage building that could double as a workshop. Convenient features include a 2-car carport with easy access to the kitchen. This home is ideally located near restaurants, shopping centers, interstate access, and Gunter AFB. Contact your agent now to schedule a viewing!
